reviewText: Great double cd from the most underrated band out there! Do not hesitate to buy this cd; top-notch musicianship and the "best" feel for music you will ever hear!

Much better then the new 2015 that is going back

performance wise there great Steve Morse clone big time
that's ok cause Steve puts nothing out anyway
Husband loves all of the band music. Listens to them all the time now. Has bought all the CD's.
